createdDate.description: The time stamp for when this seed lot was created

lastUpdated.description: The timestamp for the last update to this Seed Lot (including transactions)

locationDbId.description: The unique identifier for a Location

locationName.description: A human readable name for a location

programDbId.description: The unique DbId of the breeding program this Seed Lot belongs to

programName.description: The human readable name of the breeding program this Seed Lot belongs to

seedLotDbId.description: Unique DbId for the Seed Lot

seedLotDescription.description: A general description of this Seed Lot

seedLotName.description: A human readable name for this Seed Lot

sourceCollection.description: The description of the source where this material was originally collected (wild, nursery, etc)

units.description: Description of the things being counted in this Seed Lot (seeds, bulbs, kg, tree, etc)
